{"type": "article", "id": 26357, "title": "阿夸维特酒包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-04T07:19:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 72, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702130810uRl85UPYNTpx62kW.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">阿夸维特酒是斯堪的纳维亚地区的一种烈酒，挪威的设计公司 <a href=\"http://www.kindnorway.com/\">Kind</a> 在接到 Oss 工艺酿酒厂的委托之后，设计了以黑色为基调的外包装，传递出北欧的凛冽感以及神秘的气质。然而，当你旋转酒瓶就能发现背面印刷着色彩鲜艳的图像，这种强烈的反差正如 Kind 形容的斯堪的纳维亚人：就像椰子一样，外表坚硬冰冷，内在柔软甜蜜。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130808zY2gTIvfNXjZUq8m.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130809ucXhNnikqLYZfOsm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130809KlhG3SCYmqkUwOuQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130810S8ZsNbTo5zlBfGMa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}